Para inicializar el proyecto use npx create-react-app 

Utilizare React redux-tooklkit me parecio la manera mas facil de abordar Redux

https://redux-toolkit.js.org/tutorials/quick-start

npm install @reduxjs/toolkit react-redux

Paso 1 Create a Redux Store src/app/store.js
Paso 2 Using the provider to manage the state from the store
    this way we create a context for all the app
Paso 3 Create a Redux State Slice  src/features/counter/counterSlice.js
    create a Reducers , allow update the state, and set a new state
